"Fables is an ongoing monthly comic book series, published by Vertigo, an imprint of DC Comics. Its story concerns the lives and adventures of well-known characters from fairy tales and folklore who've been driven out of their magical homelands by a mysterious conqueror known only as the Adversary and have fled to our mundane world, where they live in the heart of New York City, in the secret exile community they call Fabletown."
